This sample builds on top of the "faciallandmarks" graph to demonstrate how to
use NvDsGazeExt extensions for interoperability with non-DS GXF components.

The graph contains additional  "NvDsVideoTemplate", "NvDsGazeTemplateLib" and
"NvDsGxfGazeDataTranslator" components required to estimate human gaze and
translate between gaze user metadata and the GXF messages.

================================================================================
Pre-requisites
================================================================================
- DeepStreamSDK 6.1
- Graph-Composer 1.0.0
- Sync extensions from NGC public repo if not already done:
    $ registry repo sync -n ngc-public

================================================================================
Download models for gaze
================================================================================
1. sudo mkdir -p /opt/nvidia/deepstream/deepstream-6.1/samples/models/tao_pretrained_models/gazenet
2. sudo wget --content-disposition https://api.ngc.nvidia.com/v2/models/nvidia/tao/gazenet/versions/deployable_v1.0/files/model.etlt \
    -O /opt/nvidia/deepstream/deepstream-6.1/samples/models/tao_pretrained_models/gazenet/gazenet_facegrid.etlt

Refer https://github.com/NVIDIA-AI-IOT/deepstream_tao_apps/tree/release/tao3.0/apps/tao_others#readme
for more info.

================================================================================
Running the graph
================================================================================
$ export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:/opt/nvidia/deepstream/deepstream-6.1/lib/cvcore_libs/
$ chmod 775 /opt/nvidia/deepstream/deepstream-6.1/samples/models/tao_pretrained_models/facenet
$ chmod 775 /opt/nvidia/deepstream/deepstream-6.1/samples/models/tao_pretrained_models/faciallandmarks
$ chmod 775 /opt/nvidia/deepstream/deepstream-6.1/samples/models/tao_pretrained_models/gazenet
For x86_64 platform
$ /opt/nvidia/graph-composer/execute_graph.sh App-Gaze.yaml App-Gaze.parameters.yaml -d /opt/nvidia/deepstream/deepstream-6.1/reference_graphs/common/target_x86_64.yaml
For Jetson
$ /opt/nvidia/graph-composer/execute_graph.sh App-Gaze.yaml App-Gaze.parameters.yaml -d /opt/nvidia/deepstream/deepstream-6.1/reference_graphs/common/target_aarch64.yaml

NOTE: App-Gaze.yaml is the main graph file describing the DeepStream
graph(pipeline) along with the configuration parameters for the components in the
graph. App-Gaze.parameters.yaml can be used to override these parameter values.
